Panda Club Madrid

  • panda_club_3.jpg
  • panda_club_4.jpg
  • panda_club.jpg
  • panda_club_2.jpg

Description

Information

Near the area of Nuevos Ministerios and the Paseo de la Castellana, this is one of Madrid’s biggest night spots, with sessions that play a wide variety of music, from reggaeton to techno house,  electronic music and the major commercial hits of the moment, with leading DJs at the decks, such as Ardiya, Luiggi López and KPD, among others.

Panda Club also has a restaurant where you can enjoy a Mediterranean menu with a few Asian highlights. In the middle of the night, there is also free food for customers.

The club is divided into two zones with different musical styles, private sections located on both sides of the central dance floor, and VIP areas right next to the DJ booth. For private events, there is an exclusive space you can hire, which is separate from the rest of the club.

The decor has an underground feel, but chic and sophisticated, like a London club. It also has a dress code.
